title: The List with Colleen Lopez 09.21.2017 - 10 PM
description:
This week, we're bringing you fashion innovation featuring PreHeals Blister Prevention Spray, Rhonda Shear, Bzees, Lysse, and more! Curator and host Colleen Lopez takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.

Watch every Thursday at 9 pm ET. *Prices shown on the previously recorded video may not represent the current price. Visit http://www.hsn.com to view the current selling price.
